azureResourceGraph.query:
resources
| where type == "microsoft.digitaltwins/digitaltwinsinstances" and name == "$ADT"
| project location, sku=tostring(sku.name), provisioningState=tostring(properties.provisioningState), created=format_datetime(todatetime(properties.createdTime), 'yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm'), updated=format_datetime(todatetime(properties.lastUpdatedTime), 'yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm'), hostName=tostring(properties.hostName)

azureLogAnalytics.query:
union ADTDigitalTwinsOperation,
ADTModelsOperation,
ADTQueryOperation
| where _ResourceId contains "$ADT"
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend Operation = tostring(split(OperationName, 'Microsoft.DigitalTwins/')[1])
| summarize Response=avg(tolong(DurationMs)) by Operation
| order by Response desc

ADTQueryOperation
| where _ResourceId contains "$ADT"
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Response=avg(tolong(DurationMs)), Count=count() by OperationName, TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

union ADTDigitalTwinsOperation,
ADTModelsOperation,
ADTQueryOperation
| where _ResourceId contains "$ADT"
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend Operation = tostring(split(OperationName, 'Microsoft.DigitalTwins/')[1])
| summarize Count=count(), Response=avg(tolong(DurationMs)) by Operation
| order by Response desc 
| project-away Response

ADTModelsOperation
| where _ResourceId contains "$ADT"
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Response=avg(tolong(DurationMs)), Count=count() by OperationName, TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

ADTDigitalTwinsOperation
| where _ResourceId contains "$ADT"
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Response=avg(tolong(DurationMs)), Count=count() by OperationName, TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

union ADTModelsOperation,
ADTQueryOperation
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
 | where _ResourceId contains "$ADT"
| summarize TotalDuration=sum(tolong(DurationMs)), Operations=count(), SpanIds=make_set(SpanId), OperationTypes=make_set(Type) by TraceId
| order by TotalDuration desc 
| take 5
